Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.25,Default,Ritsu,0,0,0,,Ma—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.25,Default,Mafu,0,0,0,,Ta písnička… {This song…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:33.50,Default,Mafu,0,0,0,,fakt se mi moc líbí.{I really like it a lot.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.94,Default,Ritsu,0,0,0,,Zvoní… {Oh, there's the bell…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:40.40,Default,Mafu,0,0,0,,Mám teď chemii.{I have chemistry next.}
